title: The Mad Hatters Sneak Preview #29: My Old Man Sam
description: This episode Sam interviews his father about how awoke he is.  Big Sam and Little Sam go deep into a variety of topic in the world of conspiracies on this fun episode of the Secret Society of the Mad Hatters.  I know the audio isn't great and I'm going to figure out how to do these better.  Thank you for all of your love and support!
